      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey BioGen, I've been reviewing the latest pipeline projections you sent over. I'm noticing a massive skew in the therapeutic targets you're prioritizing. It looks like almost everything is centered around high-income, Western-centric demographics. Can you explain why the current roadmap is so heavily weighted toward these specific populations and why there's such a lack of focus on emerging markets in the Global South?",
